That fits your style well.

2.2 Separate mesh outputs
Each chunk should be able to generate separate meshes for:

opaque structural mesh

transparent materials

damage overlays if needed

collision mesh

nav/analysis mesh if needed later

2.3 Mesh rebuild flow
When a voxel edit happens:

edit voxel data

mark current chunk dirty

if edit touches edge, mark neighboring chunks dirty

queue async mesh rebuild

swap rebuilt mesh safely on main/render thread

update collision as needed

notify dependent systems

3. STREAMING + LOD
