3.2 LOD levels
A practical model:

LOD0
Full editable chunk near player.

LOD1
Reduced mesh fidelity nearby-mid distance.

LOD2
Simplified silhouette mass.

LOD3
Very coarse proxy / impostor for distant asteroid or station chunks.

