data/contracts/contracts.json → data/missions/contracts/*

data/corporations/corporations.json → data/factions/factions.json

Final rule set
The final schema logic is:

If the data describes:
mass

terrain

hull

breach

mining

repair surface

It belongs in voxel/world schemas.

If the data describes:
device

machine

weapon

airlock

terminal

reactor

tool

It belongs in module schemas.

If the data describes:
reusable assembly

room section

ship hull section

station section

derelict section

It belongs in blueprint schemas.

If the data describes:
prices

rewards

jobs

progression

skills

factions

It belongs in economy/progression/gameplay schemas.

